---
title: "RAG — Background Embedding Worker"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Worker
    participant RAGRepository
    participant RAGService
    participant NotesRepository
    participant DB
    participant EmbeddingAPI as Embedding API

    Note over Worker: Runs on interval (embedding_queue_interval_seconds)

    Worker->>RAGRepository: get_pending_tasks(limit=20)
    RAGRepository->>DB: SELECT embedding_queue WHERE status='pending'
    DB-->>RAGRepository: tasks[]

    alt no tasks
        Worker->>Worker: sleep(interval)
    else tasks found
        loop for each task
            Worker->>RAGRepository: mark_processing(task_id)
            RAGRepository->>DB: UPDATE embedding_queue SET status='processing'

            Worker->>RAGService: embed_note(note_id, user_id)

            RAGService->>NotesRepository: get_note_by_id(note_id, user_id)
            NotesRepository->>DB: SELECT notes
            DB-->>NotesRepository: note

            RAGService->>RAGRepository: delete_chunks_for_note(note_id)
            RAGRepository->>DB: DELETE note_chunks

            RAGService->>RAGService: chunk_text(content, title)
            Note right of RAGService: Splits into overlapping<br/>chunks by token size

            RAGService->>RAGRepository: create_chunks(chunk_objs)
            RAGRepository->>DB: INSERT note_chunks (no embeddings yet)

            RAGService->>RAGRepository: get_chunks_for_note(note_id)
            RAGRepository->>DB: SELECT note_chunks
            DB-->>RAGRepository: chunks[]

            RAGService->>EmbeddingAPI: create_embeddings(texts[])
            EmbeddingAPI-->>RAGService: embeddings[]

            RAGService->>RAGRepository: set_chunk_embeddings(chunk_ids, embeddings)
            RAGRepository->>DB: UPDATE note_chunks SET embedding=...

            Worker->>RAGRepository: mark_done(task_id)
            RAGRepository->>DB: UPDATE embedding_queue SET status='done'

            alt error during embed_note
                Worker->>RAGRepository: mark_failed(task_id, error, attempts+1)
                RAGRepository->>DB: UPDATE embedding_queue SET status='failed'
            end
        end
    end
